PBSPro
```json
{
  "application": "PBSPro",
  "description": "This script converts NQS scripts to PBSPro format. It handles various NQS options and resource requests, translating them to their corresponding PBSPro equivalents.",
  "dependencies": [
    "nawk"
  ],
  "resource_requirements": [
    "Access to the PBSPro environment and its commands."
  ],
  "usage": "This script takes one or two arguments: \n\n1.  `--version` to print the version of PBSPro\n2.  `NQSscript [PBSscript]` to convert the NQS script to a PBSPro script. \n\nIf no output script is specified, the script will be written to a file named `[NQSscript].new`."
}
```
